MODIFICATIONS AND ADDITIONS TO AIDER

The following significant changes and additions have been made to create
Flaco AI from the original Aider codebase:

v1.1.0-v1.9.0 (Open Source Foundation):
--------------------------------------------
1. iOS-Specific Code Analyzers (405+ automated checks):
   - SecurityAnalyzer (50+ checks for iOS security)
   - PerformanceAnalyzer (45+ checks for iOS performance)
   - QualityAnalyzer (60+ checks for Swift code quality)
   - ArchitectureAnalyzer (40+ checks for iOS architecture)
   - SwiftUIAnalyzer (40+ checks for SwiftUI best practices)
   - IOSVersionAnalyzer (55+ checks for deprecated APIs)
   - IOSSymbolsAnalyzer (30+ checks for SF Symbols)
   - IOSHIGAnalyzer (35+ checks for HIG compliance)
   - IOSPlistAnalyzer (20+ checks for Info.plist security)
   - SPMAnalyzer (25+ checks for Package.swift quality)
   - DocumentationAnalyzer (30+ checks for doc coverage)

2. Enhanced Code Review System (v2.0.0):
   - Structured review output (Executive Summary, severity sections)
   - Interactive fix application system
   - CI/CD integration (JSON output, exit codes)
   - Baseline tracking for progress monitoring
   - GitHub issues export functionality
   - Custom team rules engine (.flaco/rules.yaml)
   - Smart context loading (generated code detection)

3. New Modules Created:
   - flacoai/analyzers/* (11 analyzer modules, ~3,500 lines)
   - flacoai/baseline_manager.py (175 lines)
   - flacoai/fix_applicator.py (262 lines)
   - flacoai/integrations/github_exporter.py (174 lines)
   - flacoai/smart_context.py (305 lines)
   - flacoai/doc_generators/* (2 modules, 680 lines)

4. Enhanced Existing Modules:
   - flacoai/coders/review_coder.py (integrated all analyzers)
   - flacoai/coders/review_prompts.py (structured output format)
   - flacoai/commands.py (new /review flags and modes)

v3.0.0 (Premium Features - Proprietary):
--------------------------------------------
5. Premium Analyzers (200+ additional checks):
   - CrashPredictionAnalyzer (proprietary)
   - PerformanceProfilerAnalyzer (proprietary)
   - MemoryLeakAnalyzer (proprietary)
   - SecurityScoringAnalyzer (proprietary)
   - TechnicalDebtAnalyzer (proprietary)

6. Commercial Features:
   - License validation system
   - Feature tier management (Free/Pro/Enterprise)
   - LaunchDarkly integration for feature flags
   - GitHub App for automatic PR reviews
   - Team metrics dashboard
   - Advanced auto-fix capabilities

================================================================================

THIRD-PARTY DEPENDENCIES

Flaco AI uses the following third-party libraries and services:

From Aider (Apache 2.0):
- Core AI integration framework
- Git repository management
- File editing and diff generation
- Prompt engineering system
- IO and terminal handling

Additional Dependencies:
- Claude AI (Anthropic) - AI model integration
- Ollama - Local LLM support
- tree-sitter - Code parsing
- PyYAML - Configuration parsing
- LaunchDarkly (optional) - Feature flags

See requirements.txt for complete list of Python dependencies.

